# Used by scraper/image_host.py to re-host Bandai card images in our own
# Supabase Storage bucket (card-images), so LinkPear can load them cross-origin.
# SUPABASE_URL: Project Settings > API > Project URL
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY: Project Settings > API > service_role secret
#   (NOT the anon/publishable key — this one bypasses RLS for uploads, so
#   keep it out of any client-facing code and never commit the real value)
